 <datafield tag="245" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
  <subfield code="a">Wigner law for matrices with dependent entries—a perturbative approach</subfield>
  <subfield code="9">IOP</subfield>
 </datafield>
 <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
  <subfield code="a">We show that Wigner semi-circle law holds for Hermitian matrices with dependent entries, provided the deviation of the cumulants from the normalised Gaussian case obeys a simple power law bound in the size of the matrix. To establish this result, we use replicas interpreted as a zero-dimensional quantum field theoretical model whose effective potential obey a renormalisation group equation.</subfield>
  <subfield code="9">IOP</subfield>
 </datafield>
